    "## - Microsoft\n",
    "\n",
    "## Microsoft demonstrates strong and consistent growth across all key financial metrics. Revenue and net income show significant year-over-year increases, indicating a stable and scalable business model. The steady rise in operating cash flow further supports its financial strength and operational efficiency.\n",
    "\n",
    "## - Tesla\n",
    "\n",
    "## Tesla exhibits a more volatile performance trend. While revenue growth is relatively modest, net income shows a decline in the most recent year. This suggests potential challenges in maintaining profitability despite growth in assets and operations. Tesla’s financials indicate a company still undergoing fluctuations in performance.\n",
    "\n",
    "## - Apple\n",
    "\n",
    "## Apple shows moderate but stable growth. Both revenue and net income increase steadily over the years, reflecting a mature and well-established business. The consistency in operating cash flow highlights strong financial management and sustained profitability."
